## How to Compile and Run

### Requirements
- C++ compiler (g++ recommended)
- Windows OS (offline operation supported)
- VS Code with C/C++ extension (recommended IDE)

### Compile
```bash
g++ main.cpp -o attendance.exe
```

### Run
```bash
./attendance.exe
```

