## Data File Formats

### students.txt
One student per line, pipe-delimited:
```
EE/22/001|Kwame|Asante|HND Electrical Engineering
EE/22/002|Ama|Owusu|HND Electrical Engineering
```

### sessions.txt
Block format per session:
```
SESSION|EEE227|2026-02-23|08:00|2
RECORD|EE/22/001|Kwame Asante|Present
RECORD|EE/22/002|Ama Owusu|Absent
END_SESSION
```

